<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10437950>
    dc:description "FIGURE 43. Collected specimens (A, B), and distribution in southeastern Brazil and adjacent areas (C, D). A. Rhagovelia robusta, apterous male from Angra dos Reis, Rio de Janeiro (−23.1414, −44.2987). B. Rhagovelia scitula, apterous male from Sapucaia, Rio de Janeiro (−22.1004, −42.7988), abdominal tergum VIII and genital capsule removed. C. Rhagovelia robusta. D. Rhagovelia scitula. Stars indicate new records; circles indicate previous records. Scale bars: 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10437950/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

